### MEDIUM Severity Findings

#### 5. Eager Test
**Test:** `OrderProcessor_FullWorkflow_Succeeds` (line 52)  
**Evidence:** Calls **7 distinct production methods** (`ValidateOrder`, `CalculateTotal`, `ApplyDiscount`, `ReserveInventory`, `ProcessPayment`, `SendConfirmation`, `UpdateOrderHistory`). A failure in any one is hard to diagnose.

**Fix:** Test each method individually; if an end-to-end workflow test is needed, name it as an integration test and document the scope.

