### Prioritized Remediation Plan

| Priority | Smell | Effort | Rationale |
|----------|-------|--------|-----------|
| 1 | Assertion-Free Test | 5 min | False-pass risk — test provides zero signal |
| 2 | Conditional Test Logic | 10 min | Hidden gap — one branch never exercises |
| 3 | Mystery Guest | 5 min | Guaranteed CI failure on non-Windows |
| 4 | Sleepy Test | 10 min | 2s wasted per run + flakiness risk |
| 5 | Exception Handling | 5 min | Mechanical replacement with `ThrowsException` |
| 6 | Sensitive Equality | 10 min | Requires knowing summary object structure |
| 7 | Magic Number Test | 10 min | Readability; derive values from inputs |
| 8 | Eager Test | 20 min | Needs test decomposition |
| 9 | General Fixture | 2 min | Remove unused field |
| 10 | Assertion Roulette | 5 min | Add message params |

